Job Description
This is an exciting opportunity to work with one of the leading shipbuilders in the OSV market. With a number of high-profile projects currently underway, my client is also tendering for further exciting and challenging projects to fill up the order books. As a result they are seeking to build their team in the Singapore office.As the successful candidate, you will have a background in Naval Architecture and hands-on experience working on basic and/or detailed designs across a selection of offshore support vessels. You will provide technical leadership and perform arrangement plans & analysis including but not limited to - stability calculation, tonnage calculation, resistance calculation, speed-power prediction and hydrostatic calculation.If this sounds like a opportunity you are interested in, please contact Ambrose Chan at
